val content = spark.sql("""with base as
(
	select  
		*,
		case when state_specific_data.email_specific_data.event_type = 'Sent' then notification_date else null end as sent_date
	from
		egdp_prod_communications.message_state_changed_domain_event_v2 where notification_date>='2022-07-01'
						
),
windowed as
(
	select
		event_header,
		event_header.event_uuid as event_uuid,
		state_specific_data.email_specific_data.parallaxed_email_address AS parallaxed_email_address,
		state_specific_data.email_specific_data.event_type AS event_type,
		notification_id,timestamp,status,
		state_specific_data,
		event_timestamp,
		notification_date,
		partner_id,
		first_value(sent_date, true) over 
		(partition by notification_id,state_specific_data.email_specific_data.recipient_id) as sent_date
		from base
),

mscde_base as
(
	select 
		notification_id,
		state_specific_data.email_specific_data.recipient_id as recipient_id,
		collect_list(distinct parallaxed_email_address) as parallaxed_email_addresses,
		sum(case when event_type = 'Sent' then 1 else 0 end) as delivered_raw,
		sum(case when event_type = 'Open' then 1 else 0 end) as opens_raw,
		sum(case when event_type = 'Bounce' then 1 else 0 end) as bounces_raw,
		sum(case when event_type = 'Click' then 1 else 0 end) as clicks_raw,
		sum(case when event_type = 'Unsubscribe' then 1 else 0 end) as unsubscribes_raw,
		sum(case when event_type = 'SpamComplaint' then 1 else 0 end) as SpamComplaints_raw,
		
		sum(case when event_type = 'Sent' and first_activity_ind=1 then 1 else 0 end) as delivered,
		sum(case when event_type = 'Open' and first_activity_ind=1 then 1 else 0 end) as opens,
		sum(case when event_type = 'Bounce' and first_activity_ind=1 then 1 else 0 end) as bounces,
		sum(case when event_type = 'Click' and first_activity_ind=1 then 1 else 0 end) as clicks,
		sum(case when event_type = 'Unsubscribe' and first_activity_ind=1 then 1 else 0 end) as unsubscribes,
		sum(case when event_type = 'SpamComplaint' and first_activity_ind=1 then 1 else 0 end) as SpamComplaints,
		
		max(case when event_type= 'Open' then cast(FROM_UNIXTIME(event_timestamp/1000) as timestamp) else null end) as max_timestamp_opens,
		max(case when event_type= 'Bounce' then cast(FROM_UNIXTIME(event_timestamp/1000) as timestamp) else null end) as max_timestamp_bounces,
		max(case when event_type= 'Click' then cast(FROM_UNIXTIME(event_timestamp/1000) as timestamp) else null end) as max_timestamp_clicks,
		max(case when event_type= 'Unsubscribe' then cast(FROM_UNIXTIME(event_timestamp/1000) as timestamp) else null end) as max_timestamp_unsubs,
		max(case when event_type= 'SpamComplaint' then cast(FROM_UNIXTIME(event_timestamp/1000) as timestamp) else null end) as max_timestamp_spamcomplaints,
		max(cast(FROM_UNIXTIME(event_timestamp/1000) as timestamp)) as max_timestamp,
		min(sent_date) as sent_date
		
		from 
		(
			select *,
			row_number() 
			OVER (PARTITION BY notification_id,state_specific_data.email_specific_data.recipient_id,sent_date,event_type,date(cast(FROM_UNIXTIME(event_timestamp/1000) as timestamp))
			ORDER BY cast(FROM_UNIXTIME(event_timestamp/1000) as timestamp)) AS first_activity_ind from windowed
		)
		group by 1,2
),

message_tracking_egdp as 
(
    select * from egdp_prod_communications.message_tracking_domain_event_v1
    where status = 'HANDED_OFF_TO_VENDOR'

)

select 
A.notification_id,
A.recipient_id,
A.parallaxed_email_addresses,
B.tracking_code.attribution as email_omni_code,
A.delivered_raw + A.bounces_raw as attempted_raw,
A.delivered_raw,
A.opens_raw,
A.bounces_raw,
A.clicks_raw,
A.unsubscribes_raw,
A.SpamComplaints_raw,
A.delivered + A.bounces  as attempted,
A.delivered,
A.opens,
A.bounces,
A.clicks,
A.unsubscribes,
A.SpamComplaints,
A.max_timestamp_opens,
A.max_timestamp_bounces,
A.max_timestamp_clicks,
A.max_timestamp_unsubs,
A.max_timestamp_spamcomplaints,
A.max_timestamp,
A.sent_date
from 
mscde_base  A 
join
message_tracking_egdp B 
on A.recipient_id = B.eg_account_id
and A.notification_id = B.notification_id""")
